					<li>weather_fog_outdoors(INITIATOR_mood>=0.3,INITIATOR_mood&lt;0.5)->This fog won't let me see a damn thing.</li>
					<li>weather_fog_outdoors(INITIATOR_mood&lt;0.3)->Blasted fog! Can't see a bloody thing out here!</li>
					<!--Recipient's hunting skill-->
